  <brief_title>An Observational Study of MabThera/Rituxan (Rituximab) in Patients With Follicular Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Observational Phase IV Non Interventional Study in Patients With Advanced Follicular Lymphoma (III-IV) Evaluating the Safety of Maintenance Therapy With Rituximab After 8 Cycles of Rituximab in Combination With Chemotherapy as Induction Therapy in Previously Untreated Patients in Greece.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
